.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/180352/', '', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, Siponimod, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, More', 'Brivaracetam, Topiramate, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Lamotrigine, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, Oxcarbazepine, Ethotoin, Rufinamide, More', 1767369485);
